<div class="setup-access">
  <h2 class="setup-access__page-header">{{t "Selecting Buttons" key="selecting_buttons_header"}}</h2>
  {{! Top card: How will this communicator be selecting buttons? — options left, display right }}
  <div class="setup-access__card">
    <div class="setup-access__card-row">
      <div class="setup-access__card-left">
        <h3 class="setup-access__question">{{t "How will this communicator be selecting buttons?" key="access_selection"}}</h3>
        <div class="setup-access__radios" role="radiogroup" aria-label={{t "How will this communicator be selecting buttons?" key="access_selection"}}>
          <button type="button" class="setup-access__radio {{if this.setup.access.touch "is-selected"}}" role="radio" aria-checked={{this.setup.access.touch}} {{action "set_preference" "access" "touch" target=this.setup}}>
            <span class="setup-access__radio-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="setup-access__radio-label">{{t "Touching or Clicking" key="touching_or_clicking"}}</span>
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="setup-access__radio {{if this.setup.access.scanning "is-selected"}}" role="radio" aria-checked={{this.setup.access.scanning}} {{action "set_preference" "access" "scanning" target=this.setup}}>
            <span class="setup-access__radio-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="setup-access__radio-label">{{t "Scanning Using a Switch" key="switch_access"}}</span>
          </button>
          <button type="button" class="setup-access__radio {{if this.setup.access.dwell "is-selected"}}" role="radio" aria-checked={{this.setup.access.dwell}} {{action "set_preference" "access" "dwell" target=this.setup}}>
            <span class="setup-access__radio-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="setup-access__radio-label">{{t "Eye or Dwell Tracking" key="dwell_tracking"}}</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="setup-access__card-right">
        {{#if this.setup.access.touch}}
          <div class="setup-access__display">
            <div class="setup-access__display-media">
              <img src={{path "walkthrough/aac_intro.gif"}} alt={{t "touch access to %app_name%" key="touch_access"}} class="setup-access__img">
            </div>
            <p class="setup-access__display-p">
              <span class="setup-access__display-icon glyphicon glyphicon-hand-up" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              {{t "In %app_name%, touch or tap is the standard way to use boards: move between boards and select words or phrases for the app to speak." key="touch_1"}}
            </p>
            <p class="setup-access__display-p">{{t "You can customize the experience in Preferences—selection on finger lift, larger text, and spacing between buttons are all available." key="touch_2"}}</p>
          </div>
        {{else if this.setup.access.scanning}}
          <div class="setup-access__display">
            <div class="setup-access__display-media">
              <img src={{path "walkthrough/scanning.gif"}} alt={{t "scanning access in %app_name%" key="scanning_access"}} class="setup-access__img">
            </div>
            <p class="setup-access__display-p">
              <span class="setup-access__display-icon glyphicon glyphicon-th" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              {{t "When small buttons are hard to use, %app_name% can use a switch or a tap on the screen instead. The app breaks the board into smaller chunks and scans through them one at a time—you select with your switch." key="scanning_1"}}
            </p>
            <p class="setup-access__display-p">{{t "You can scan by row, column, or custom region, and adjust voice or volume for scanning. External switches, a full-screen button, or two buttons are all available in Preferences." key="scanning_2"}}</p>
          </div>
        {{else}}
          <div class="setup-access__display">
            <div class="setup-access__display-media">
              <img src={{path "walkthrough/eye_gaze.gif"}} alt={{t "dwell access in %app_name%" key="dwell_access"}} class="setup-access__img">
            </div>
            <p class="setup-access__display-p">
              <span class="setup-access__display-icon glyphicon glyphicon-eye-open" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              {{t "When motor control is limited, eye or dwell tracking can help—the system selects when your gaze or cursor lingers on a button. It can be faster than switch access but often needs careful calibration." key="dwell_1"}}
            </p>
            <p class="setup-access__display-p">{{t "%app_name% works with any eye tracker or system that supports cursor control. Disable \"click\" events so the app handles selection. You can fine-tune tracking in Preferences; some devices need extra setup there as well." key="dwell_2"}}</p>
          </div>
        {{/if}}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  {{! Bottom card: What happens when the communicator selects a button? — question, text, radio options }}
  <div class="setup-access__card">
    <h3 class="setup-access__question">{{t "What happens when the communicator selects a button?" key="access_selection_action"}}</h3>
    <p class="setup-access__prompt">{{t "After each tap, %app_name% can return to the home board. That consistent sequence (a motor plan) helps many communicators—we recommend it, but you can change it in Preferences." key="home_return_1"}}</p>
    <div class="setup-access__radios" role="radiogroup" aria-label={{t "What happens when the communicator selects a button?" key="access_selection_action"}}>
      <button type="button" class="setup-access__radio {{if this.setup.home_return.auto_return "is-selected"}}" role="radio" aria-checked={{this.setup.home_return.auto_return}} {{action "set_preference" "home_return" "auto_return" target=this.setup}}>
        <span class="setup-access__radio-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="setup-access__radio-label">{{t "Return to the Home Board" key="return_to_the_home_board"}}</span>
      </button>
      <button type="button" class="setup-access__radio {{if this.setup.home_return.stay "is-selected"}}" role="radio" aria-checked={{this.setup.home_return.stay}} {{action "set_preference" "home_return" "stay" target=this.setup}}>
        <span class="setup-access__radio-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="setup-access__radio-label">{{t "Stay on the Current Board" key="stay_on_the_current_board"}}</span>
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
